{"tid":2020184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：指控監警會報告漂白人士立心不良！","createTime":"2020-05-17T00:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T02:56:38.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dce128459b25b187e4432c31625b35cb86830b18","tid":2020184,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52003d1efdc742769d7bb2cb37186595a75e446","tid":2020184,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T00:24:47.000Z","msg":"政務司長張建宗發表網誌，指監警會公開審視報告後，坊間有人指控報告「撐警」、「扶警」、為警方「漂白」，認為言論再次顯示某些立心不良的人，非要打撃警隊不可。<br />\n<br />\n他指，監警會作為法定獨立機構，過去十個月來經過嚴謹、深入、客觀、詳細審視，釐清事實真相，是其是，非其非，提出52項客觀而具建設性的建議，特區政府整體接納監警會的建議，會由保安局局長成立專責小組認真研究和跟進，指市民不應輕信網上流傳的片面及誤導性的訊息甚至虛假指控，呼籲大家回歸理性，對報告作公道及中肯評價，強調香港要向暴力說不。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1287997&amp;PageSpeed=noscript\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1287997%26PageSpeed%3Dnoscript&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e617tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=bd483c11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1287997&amp;PageSpeed=noscript</a>"},{"pid":"0749d1f491fec5804b4adff158ab9f2cd1adcd02","tid":2020184,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T00:25:29.000Z","msg":"張建宗本人都「撐警」"},{"pid":"f062955bba0776fcf17db716123053b450eb35fb","tid":2020184,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T00:26:20.000Z","msg":"講真 就算三萬個坐曬監<br />\n大家會服氣咩？"},{"pid":"be807035a39836440099adbcf780f9a1599fc455","tid":2020184,"uid":274722,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T00:26:58.000Z","msg":"成份報告冇提過警暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c